* **`<html>`** â†’ Root element of the document.
* **`<head>`** â†’ Contains metadata and links CSS files.
* **`<link>`** â†’ Connects external CSS file and Bootstrap.
* **`<body>`** â†’ Contains visible content.
* **`<div>`** â†’ Background container (`.bg`) and card container (`.card-container`).
* **`<h1>`** â†’ Main heading (â€œAdvanced Technologiesâ€).
* **`<p>`** â†’ Description under the heading.
* **`<button>`** â†’ Call-to-action buttons (â€œLearn Moreâ€ and â€œSave Draftâ€).

