# ğŸ”¹ CSS Properties I Used

* **`background-image`** â†’ Sets the hero section background.
* **`background-size`** â†’ Ensures background covers the container fully.
* **`height` / `width`** â†’ Controls size of background and card containers.
* **`font-family`** â†’ Applies custom fonts like Roboto and Bree Serif.
* **`font-size`** / **`font-style`** / **`font-weight`** â†’ Styles headings and description.
* **`color`** â†’ Sets text color for heading, description, and buttons.
* **`padding`** â†’ Adds spacing inside card container and buttons.
* **`margin`** â†’ Adds spacing between buttons and elements.
* **`border-radius`** â†’ Rounds corners of card container and buttons.
* **Bootstrap Flex (`d-flex`, `flex-column`, `flex-row`, `justify-content-end`)** â†’ Positions card at the bottom and arranges buttons horizontally.
* **`background-color`** â†’ Colors card container and buttons for contrast.

